  Update Model Permissions

  1. Ask for approval     Codex can read and edit files in the current
                          workspace, and run commands. Approval is required to
                          access the internet or edit other files.
     Auto (disabled)      Auto-review approves routine local work and denies
                          or escalates unsafe actions. (disabled: invalid
                          value for `approvals_reviewer`: `AutoReview` is not
                          in the allowed set [User] (set by <unspecified>))
  2. Full Access          Codex can edit files outside this workspace and
                          access the internet without asking for approval.
                          Exercise caution when using.
› 3. Read Only (current)  Codex can read files in the current workspace.
                          Approval is required to edit files or access the
                          internet.

  Press enter to confirm or esc to go back
